This demonstrates that curvature alone is sufficient to induce global coherence, without exchange forces, bosonic statistics, or environmental coupling.
The result provides direct numerical validation of the Motionâ€“TimeSpace (MBT) field equation claim:
Matter and coherence emerge from geometry, not particle interaction.

